query: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, IDoc.Number Ent from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and len(IDoc.Number) = 10 order by PerC.BirthDate
select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, IDoc.Number Ent from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 1 order by PerC.BirthDate
